    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110800/extras/d96550f994df0677ee02bb23897eb941.avif?t=1765917518\" width=600 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tailless Frank is a randomly generated roguelite deckbuilding game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Help Frank on his journey by exploring the caves, upgrading your deck and fighting enemies to find what happened to his tail.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deck Building: find the merchants, choose your cards wisely and combine them to fight the enemies. Watch out for cards that hurt you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run is unique: with random generated maps, every run will feel different.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special items: powerful items that will enhance your deck and your abilities.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enemies</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Improve your deck to fight the enemies. Look for special items that help you on your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110800/extras/dbdacdf3b13149952d55ddc3dcb53626.avif?t=1765917518\" width=600 height=206 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Merchant</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The merchant will give you an opportunity to edit your deck by buying new cards and abilities that will enhance them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110800/extras/78c34417a43d26bda0fb99a7612f9a5b.avif?t=1765917518\" width=600 height=206 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2>",
